name: Unidentified_Weequay_marksman
content:
This Weequay marksman was an assassin in the employ of Jabba Desilijic Tiure around 4 ABY. A religious Weequay, this marksman used womp rats for target practice offering them as sacrifices, in accordance with Weequay religious practices. He was present on the top-deck of the Khetanna during the Battle of the Great Pit of Carkoon where he was sliced in half by Luke Skywalker.
Glimpsed only briefly on the top-deck of the Khetanna during Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, this particular Weequay wears similar clothing to another Weequay thrown out of the Khetanna by Skywalker.
